title: Wall Street Breakfast June 10: Rule of 10: Is a Recession Near With Gas Prices at $5/Gallon?
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Rule of 10: Is a recession near with gas prices at $5/gallon? CPI preview: Inflation still sizzling, but will there be signs of relief?  Median monthly asking rents climb over $2K for first time ever, Redfin says. White House reallocating $10B away from COVID testing, PPE to ensure vaccine preparedness. Catch today’s WSB article here.
